| 2024-07-14    | V1.0    | Initial Test Strategy for Image Upload Feature | QA Director |

# 3. Scope
## 3.2.1 In Scope
- Single-file image upload via authenticated session
- API Gateway upload endpoint
- Server-side image optimization and compression
- Inline virus scanning and file validation
- PNG and JPEG file support
- AWS S3 storage integration
- Instant grid update on successful upload

## 3.2.2 Out of Scope
- Client-side image optimization or pre-processing
- Support for non-image or alternative formats (WebP, GIF, SVG, TIFF)
- Batch or multi-file uploads
- Storage on internal file servers or non-AWS S3 providers

