## 4.5 Test Data Management
### 4.5.1 Data Requirements
- PNG/JPEG files at 9.99MB, 10.00MB, 10.01MB
- Files with spoofed headers for negative testing
- Valid/invalid authentication tokens
- Test images with and without viruses

